rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f6d738de996f6e763ce2064925b9d1ab8997b3","tid":2064344,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"好好享受人生"},{"pid":"adb4bf7ac436134ab4c6976d43d2927792de9bef","tid":2064344,"uid":109050,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13b07b2651abc415b48ab70a8ce6dc7f0e8dcfe5","tid":2064344,"uid":258598,"like":24,"dislike":38,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:42:50.000Z","msg":"我夠想啦 唔返工邊個養我"},{"pid":"623ade64f06219e1bd97365c67629acac64c26fb","tid":2064344,"uid":158899,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"c06d692a845b671ff1def02f91a0b61aa330d748","tid":2064344,"uid":69841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"罷工兼罷搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90588d32cf49c1db04265934e48b8690f315bee","tid":2064344,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"045cb64f70c90f0e803c761a8fdcafa183859116","tid":2064344,"uid":348951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite